Package com.sicomsa.dmt.solicitude.batch

Class BatchWriter

java.lang.Object
com.sicomsa.dmt.solicitude.batch.BatchWriter
All Implemented Interfaces:
AutoCloseable
public class BatchWriter extends Object implements AutoCloseable
BatchWriter formats a file with a SOAPMessage containing the requests included in a Batch object, and adds the responses received from the web service to the message that is then updated in this writer's assigned file.

This writer and its file should be accessed by a single thread.

Since:
1.0
Version:
2024.12.27
Author:
Beto Lopez

  • Nested Class Summary

    Nested Classes
    Modifier and Type
    Class
    Description
    protected class 
    BatchWriter.SOAPWriter
    SOAPWriter uses a SOAPMessage prototype to add temporary content to its SOAPBodyElement using the BatchWriter.SOAPWriter.addChildElement(javax.xml.namespace.QName) method which adds elements to the body of this message tat can be appended to the BatchWriter's file using the BatchWriter.SOAPWriter.writeAppendedElement() method.
